    <text>
    <body>
        <p>Louisville, Kentucky, Belgian diplomat. Belgium native. Married Charlotte Vanderespt. Father of Walter Vanderespt. A Mason. Louisville resident since 1854. Belgian Vice Consul in Louisville. Owned a drug store in Louisville in 1858.</p>

    </body>
